g.text: In this exercise you add a trasaction type and merge all data into one table
Join the information on the onsite purchases with the information on the
product prizes (bottom output table of the metanode). Exclude columns that
were created as intermediate columns in some data manipulation steps.
Create a new column "Type" that gets the value "Store - no CC" if the
customer ID is not available, and "Store - CC" otherwise.
Create a new column "Type" with a constant value "OnlineStore" for the
orders coming from the online store (top output port of the metanode)
Concatenate the data on online and onsite purchases
